# CSV Profiler — Data Profiling Pipeline

A FastAPI + Streamlit data pipeline that ingests CSV files, extracts
and transforms data quality metrics, and delivers structured JSON reports.

---

## Pipeline Architecture

| Stage     | What happens                                      |
|-----------|---------------------------------------------------|
| Ingest    | User uploads CSV via Streamlit                    |
| Extract   | FastAPI reads file, chardet detects encoding      |
| Transform | Pandas computes stats, outliers, correlations     |
| Export    | Structured JSON report returned to frontend       |
| Deliver   | Downloadable report saved to /reports/            |

Full architecture documented in `docs/architecture.md`

---

## Features

- Upload any CSV file
- Automatic encoding detection
- Dataset overview (rows, columns, memory usage)
- Missing value analysis
- Numeric statistics (mean, median, min, max, std)
- Outlier detection using IQR
- Distribution metrics (skewness, kurtosis)
- Duplicate row detection
- Constant and empty column detection
- Correlation matrix for numeric columns
- Downloadable JSON report via /export/

---

## Tech Stack

- Backend: FastAPI, Uvicorn
- Frontend: Streamlit
- Data Processing: Pandas, NumPy
- Encoding Detection: Chardet

---

## Project Structure
```
project-root/
├── backend/
│   └── app/
│       ├── main.py       # pipeline entrypoint, API routes
│       ├── utils.py      # extraction and transformation logic
│       └── config.py     # CORS setup
├── frontend/
│   └── stream_lit.py     # Streamlit UI
├── docs/
│   └── architecture.md   # pipeline architecture documentation
├── reports/              # delivered report outputs
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

---

## Setup
```bash
python -m venv myenv
myenv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

---

## Running

Start backend:
```bash
uvicorn backend.app.main:app --reload
```

Start frontend (new terminal):
```bash
cd frontend
python -m streamlit run stream_lit.py
```

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint       | Description                        |
|--------|----------------|------------------------------------|
| GET    | /              | Health check                       |
| POST   | /upload-csv/   | Upload CSV, returns JSON report    |
| GET    | /export/       | Download last report as JSON file  |

